V
V = \{ (x, y, z)  : 0 \leq z \leq c, 0 \leq x^2 + y^2 \leq \frac12 z \}
V = \{ (x, y, z) = (r \cos \phi, r \sin \phi, z)  : 0 \leq z \leq c, 0 \leq r^2 \leq \frac12 z, 0 \leq \phi \leq 2\pi \}.
